Class DumpUtils

java.lang.Object
org.krmdemo.techlabs.core.dump.DumpUtils
public class DumpUtils extends Object
Utility-class that is a static facade of ObjectPrinter.ToString, where the serializing of an object is provided with JacksonTree.
Set of methods with the second RenderSpec arguments allow to suppress the default highlighting by providing new RenderSpec(Highlight.HONE, ...).
